-       The xpdf software and documentation are  copyright  1996-2019  Glyph  &
-       Cog, LLC.
-
-SEE ALSO
-       pdftops(1), pdftotext(1), pdftohtml(1), pdfinfo(1), pdffonts(1), pdfde-
-       tach(1), pdftoppm(1), pdftopng(1), pdfimages(1), xpdfrc(5)
-       http://www.xpdfreader.com/
